title: [Luminary Festival, High Striker]
description: Towering above the surrounding foliage, and reaching higher than the various apple trees that dot the landscape, is a tall bell-topped pole marked incrementally in black paint.  Smaller posts surrounding it are decorated with either black ribbons for failures or the blue ribbons of prize winners, their ends trailing to the moss-dappled ground.  A large wooden-hafted mallet rests against the pole, with a burly muscular huckster looking on.
